<section class="mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl px-6 py-20 border-t border-line/30">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
    <div>
      <p class="font-heading text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-sm">Our Philosophy</p>
      <h2 class="mt-4 font-heading text-4xl uppercase leading-tight">
        Scent is the Ultimate <br /> Tactical Advantage.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-muted leading-relaxed">
        We don't just make candles. We build atmospheric foundations for your game-day rituals. Every Playbook scent is engineered to evoke the grit, strategy, and triumph of the gridiron.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-heading text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-2">Drawn Up Right</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">Hand-poured with premium soy wax and custom fragrance blends designed for maximum projection.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-heading text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-2">Field Tested</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">Tested in high-pressure environments to ensure they stand up to even the most intense 4th quarters.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative">
      <div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-2xl bg-surface border-2 border-line/50 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 playbook-line"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10 text-center p-8">
          <div class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full border border-accent/30 p-4">
             <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-full bg-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-accent font-heading text-2xl">X</span>
             </div>
          </div>
          <p class="font-heading text-xl uppercase italic">"The game isn't just won on the field, it's won in the atmosphere."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
